---
title: Seared Chicken & Parmesan Potato Salad with Celery Slaw
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of classic chicken shop flavours. Tender chicken strips get a lightly spiced coating,
with a warm, creamy potato salad and a crunchy celery slaw to round out the meal.

